            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1301783</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>美国网红 IShowSpeed（甲亢哥）于 4 月 5 日抵达深圳，展开了他的中国之行。他首度体验了比亚迪仰望 U8 这款能在水中行驶的豪华吉普车，并与粉丝一同分享了惊险刺激的经历。他也在深圳的华为旗舰店疯狂购物，当场买下三部华为 Mate XT 折叠手机，并即刻开箱展示。</p><p>在直播的开场，「甲亢哥」的首个挑战是乘坐比亚迪的仰望 U8。上车前，他表现出一些不安，担心车辆会沉入水中，并询问助手是否确保他会安全。助手则提议不绑安全带，认为这样他能更快脱困。但当车子实际驶入水中时，「甲亢哥」的情绪显得非常紧张不断尖叫，他一度担心车子会沈下去，并且焦急地要求司机把车开回岸边。在成功回到沙滩后，「甲亢哥」原本打算自己试驾这辆车，但由于沙地过软，车辆无法前进。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301784" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>随后，他来到位于深圳的万象天地华为旗舰店，并对店内展示的三折叠手机 Mate XT 表现出极大兴趣。他对手机的设计赞不绝口，当场购买了三部 Mate XT，并在车上立刻开箱，不停地惊呼「这款手机太疯狂了！」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301790" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在随后的直播中，「甲亢哥」不仅与粉丝互动，还带著粉丝游览深圳的人才公园，并体验了美团的无人机外卖服务。当他看到无人机送来他点的 KFC 时，他大为惊喜。他还用手机直播了无人机配送的过程，并向粉丝介绍了中国在科技和物流领域的创新。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301787" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301788" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/irlstreaminshenzhenc-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>资料来源：IShowSpeed</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
